OL,3,CPolice officer assaulted teen who
OL,4,Csubjected him homophobic abuse
OL,6,FThe incident took place on 25 October
OL,7,F2024 at North Cheshire Custody Suite
OL,8,Fin Runcorn.
OL,10,FA 15-year-old boy was arrested and
OL,11,Ftaken into police custody, believed to
OL,12,Fbe in relation to alleged county lines
OL,13,Fdrug dealing and the possession of a
OL,14,Fknife.
OL,16,FAccording to Cheshire Police, PC
OL,17,FClarke was subjected to a "sustained
OL,18,Fperiod of homophobic abuse" by the
OL,19,Fjuvenile detainee.
