OL,6,FA notification of outcome states: "On
OL,7,FOctober 25, 2024, at North Cheshire
OL,8,FCustody Suite, following a sustained
OL,9,Fperiod of homophobic abuse from a
OL,10,Fjuvenile detainee, PC Clarke used
OL,11,Fforce against the juvenile, which was
OL,12,Fnot deemed to be reasonable,
OL,13,Fnecessary, or proportionate.
OL,15,F"Following a criminal investigation,
OL,16,Fon September 17, 2025, the officer was
OL,17,Ffound guilty of assault.
