OL,3,CPolice officer assaulted teen who
OL,4,Csubjected him homophobic abuse
OL,6,F"Constable Clarke's conduct breached
OL,7,Fthe Standards of Professional
OL,8,FBehaviour in relation to authority,
OL,9,Frespect, courtesy, use of force, and
OL,10,Fdiscreditable conduct, and he admitted
OL,11,Fthat his conduct amounted to gross
OL,12,Fmisconduct.
OL,14,F"The hearing found that he had a case
OL,15,Fto answer for gross misconduct, and he
OL,16,Fwas issued with a final written
OL,17,Fwarning for five years."
