OL,3,CPolice officer assaulted teen who
OL,4,Csubjected him homophobic abuse
OL,6,FChief Constable Mark Roberts noted in
OL,7,Fmitigation, PC Clarke's remorse, his
OL,8,Fexemplary record and service to
OL,9,Fpolicing, that it was a momentary
OL,10,Flapse of self-control and judgement
OL,11,Fand that the numerous testimonials to
OL,12,Fhis character spread over ranks spoke
OL,13,Fto his professional and positive
OL,14,Fcharacter traits.
OL,16,FHe said: "I am conscious that in case
OL,17,Fof gross misconduct for there not to
OL,18,Fbe dismissal there must be exceptional
OL,19,Fcircumstances.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
