OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F399A1765477982
OL,3,CPolice officer assaulted teen who
OL,4,Csubjected him homophobic abuse
OL,6,F"That is borne out of my approach in
OL,7,Ffour years of conducting accelerated
OL,8,Fmisconduct hearings; I have only once
OL,9,Fpreviously not dismissed an officer
OL,10,Fafter a finding of gross misconduct.
OL,12,F"I am of the view, considering
OL,13,Feverything I have read in the bundle
OL,14,Fand heard during the course of this
OL,15,Fhearing , that although the starting
OL,16,Fposition when gross misconduct is
OL,17,Fproven is dismissal, there are
OL,18,Fexceptional circumstances in this case
OL,19,Fto justify a less severe sanction,
OL,20,Fnamely a final written warning for
OL,21,Ffive years."
